item.title: Arches National Park
item.description: Wow, time really does fly. I feel like I’m only now finding my bearings since my previous post about Mount Lincoln - I have since moved from home to Edmonds to (at some point in the near future) Seattle, visited two national parks, and ventured out of North America for the first time to see the sights in Iceland. As soon as I have the opportunity to organize all my photos, I’ll be sure to expand on this post and create future posts on Mount Rainier and the scenes around ReykjavÃ­k. In the mean time, in the name of staying on a schedule, I thought I’d post this update.
